headline.print_headline: Woods Misses Fourth Major Cut as a Pro at PGA
headline.main: Woods Misses Fourth Major Cut as a Pro at PGA

lead_paragraph: A badly out-of-sorts Tiger Woods missed the fourth major cut of his professional career after again struggling with his game in the second round of the PGA Championship on Friday.
